OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright and chilly start with
OL,6,Fa touch of frost possible. Sunny
OL,7,Fspells will turn hazy during the day
OL,8,Fas cloud thickens from the west,
OL,9,Fpatchy light rain possible in the
OL,10,FTrossachs. Feeling pleasant in any
OL,11,Fsunshine with light winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FOutbreaks of rain pushing
OL,14,Feastwards, mostly light and patchy,
OL,15,Fbut the odd heavier burst possible in
OL,16,Fthe west. Turning more showery
OL,17,Fovernight, the showers mainly in the
OL,18,Fwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
