OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FBright spells and showers, the
OL,6,Fbest of the brightness for Angus,
OL,7,FDundee and Fife during the morning.
OL,8,FThe showers could be heavy, perhaps
OL,9,Fthe odd rumble of thunder.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMainly
OL,12,Fdry and bright on Monday with early
OL,13,Fshowers dying out. Rain or showers on
OL,14,FTuesday and Wednesday, heavy at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
